Barclays is Considering Increasing Stake Its in Absa, Business Day Reports

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-03-14T05:34:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/barclays-is-considering-increasing-stake-its-in-absa-business-day-reports.html
  Barclays Plc (BARC)  Chairman Marcus Agius
raised the prospect of the U.K. lender increasing its stake in
Absa Group Ltd., Business Day reported, citing Agius.  Asked to confirm reports that Barclays Chief Executive
Officer  Bob Diamond  is considering increasing the stake, Agius
said it was possible, the Johannesburg-based newspaper reported.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
